                  </hi>. I am a provision merchant, and reside in George-street. On the evening of 10th Feb., I was crossing Tower-hill, I felt my pocket moved by some one—I turned round, and saw the prisoner behind me—I laid hold of him—he said, "I have not your handkerchief"—I put my hand into his pocket, and took my handkerchief from him—this is it—it had been in my pocket.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="185202230005"></xptr>
