                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> What made you take it till the policeman came up? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Because I knew by your manner that you had got it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I had not got it.</p>
